+	 *
+	 * Purists are gonna blast me for this.
+	 * But there are so many people (read Outlook users) who want this.
+	 * And Evo is an exchange-client, Outlook-replacement etc.
+	 * So Here it goes :(
+	 *
+	 * -- Sankar
+	 *
+	 */
